Package titocc.compiler

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Symbol
    Represents a declared name like variable, function or code position.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Assembler
    Formats and writes individual instructions to the output stream.
    Compiler
    Main compiler class.
    InternalSymbol
    Class for symbols that are only used internally by the compiler, like code positions inside functions etc.
    Parser
    Main parser class.
    Scope
    Represents a scope (aka namespace) that contains symbols declared within that scope.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Register
    Enumeration of the registers in ttk-91 machine.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    InternalCompilerException
    Exception class for internal compiler errors.
